{
  "text": "Our first demonstrator application that can take advantage of our token account service is gossip learning [CITATION_1] . We present the most common, proactive implementation. The goal of this application is to learn from distributed data using stochastic gradient descent (SGD) [CITATION_2] . We assume that every node in the network has only one training example (x, y), but we can benefit from having more local data. The set of these local examples form our machine learning database. We would like to learn a model over these instances in a fully distributed manner.",
  "correct_citation": {
